  rico:scopeAndContent <https://data.archives.gov.on.test.gbad.caSeries%20consists%20of%20meeting%20and%20subscription%20records%20created%20by%20the%20Burns%20Monument%20Committee%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Committee%27s%20reports.%20%20Included%20is%20a%20minute%20book%20recording%20the%20details%20of%20Burns%20Monument%20Committee%20meetings%2C%20held%20at%20the%20following%20venues%20in%20Toronto%2C%20Ontario%3A%20the%20residence%20of%20Committee%20President%2C%20Mr.%20David%20Walker%3B%20St.%20George%27s%20Hall%3B%20the%20Crown%20Hotel%3B%20the%20McKinnon%20Building%3B%20and%20the%20Confederation%20Life%20Building.%20%20Also%20included%20are%20lists%20of%20subscribers%20to%20the%20Burns%20Monument%20Fund%2C%20indicating%20their%20amounts%20paid%2C%20as%20well%20as%20eleven%20subscription%20books%20issued%20to%20members%20of%20the%20Burns%20Monument%20Committee%2C%20authorizing%20them%20to%20obtain%20subscriptions%20in%20aid%20of%20the%20Burns%20Monument%20Fund.%20The%20books%20are%20assigned%20to%20William%20Adamson%2C%20William%20Burton%2C%20Alex%20Fraser%2C%20G.W.%20Grant%2C%20John%20Morrison%2C%20Charles%20Walker%2C%20William%20G.%20Scott%2C%20and%20Geoffrey%20Vair.%20%20The%20series%20also%20contains%20two%20reports%20from%201899%20from%20the%20Burns%20Memorial%20Fund%27s%20Committee%20on%20Printing%20and%20Supplies%20to%20the%20General%20Committee%2C%20as%20well%20as%20two%20copies%20of%20a%201904%20auditor%27s%20report%20to%20the%20president%20and%20officers%20of%20the%20Burns%20Monument%20Committee.> .

