  rico:scopeAndContent <https://data.archives.gov.on.test.gbad.caSeries%20consists%20of%20newsclippings%20which%20deal%20with%20many%20difference%20aspects%20of%20Eaton%27s%3A%20from%20store%20openings%20to%20the%20cars%20owned%20by%20the%20Eaton%20family.%20%20These%20newsclippings%20were%20microfilmed%20for%20Eaton%27s%20Archives%20Office%20between%201962%20and%201967.%20%20While%20most%20of%20the%20clippings%20are%20from%20Toronto%20papers%2C%20there%20are%20some%20from%20such%20places%20as%20PEI%20and%20Manitoba.%20%20Also%20included%20are%20a%20few%20hand-typed%20press%20releases%20from%20Eaton%27s.%20%20The%20first%20three%20reels%20of%20this%20series%2C%20containing%20clippings%20from%201896%20to%201956%2C%20are%20arranged%20chronologically.%20%20The%20remaining%20twelve%20reels%20are%20arranged%20by%20subject%20and%20year.%20%20The%20date%20range%20for%20these%20clippings%20is%201905%20to%201967.> .

