  rico:isOrWasDescribedBy <https://data.archives.gov.on.test.gbad.ca/KB/ArchivalDescriptionRecord/RG%2016-66>;
  rico:scopeAndContent <https://data.archives.gov.on.test.gbad.caSeries%20consists%20of%20the%20activity%20reports%20submitted%20annually%20by%20Agricultural%20Representatives%20across%20rural%20Ontario%20to%20their%20Branch%20office.%20The%20reports%20outline%20the%20state%20of%20the%20local%20agricultural%20economy%2C%20the%20weather%20and%20crop%20conditions%20during%20the%20past%20year%2C%20the%20representatives%27%20objectives%20for%20their%20region%2C%20a%20description%20of%20new%20projects%20or%20initiatives%20planned%2C%20and%20comments%20on%20the%20local%20effectiveness%20of%20various%20capital%20grant%20programs.%20%20The%20reports%20record%20the%20outreach%20activities%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Agriculture%20and%20Food%20and%20its%20predecessors%2C%20including%3A%20innovations%20in%20farming%20lectures%3B%20drainage%20equipment%20demonstrations%3B%20plowing%20matches%3B%20agricultural%20exhibition%20displays%3B%20and%20liaisons%20with%20the%204H%2C%20Women%27s%20Institutes%2C%20and%20various%20rural%20associations.%20%20The%20reports%20are%20arranged%20alphabetically%20by%20the%20name%20of%20the%20county%2F%20district%20and%20then%20chronologically.%20%20Several%20reports%2C%20especially%20for%20the%20years%201940-1941%2C%20are%20missing.> .

