  rico:scopeAndContent <https://data.archives.gov.on.test.gbad.caSub-%20series%20consists%20of%20case%20files%20created%20and%20maintained%20by%20the%20Sudbury%20Probation%20and%20Parole%20Office%20pertaining%20to%20young%20offenders.%20Files%20include%20memoranda%20and%20correspondence%2C%20judicial%20orders%2C%20photographs%2C%20probation%20and%20parole%20officer%20assessments%2C%20and%20action%20requests%2Fapprovals.%20The%20files%20document%20the%20inmate%27s%20previous%20criminal%20behaviour%2C%20education%2C%20work%20experience%20and%20future%20plans%2C%20as%20well%20as%20prospects%20for%20rehabilitation%20and%20integration%20in%20the%20community.%20%20Case%20files%20from%201985%20have%20been%20sampled%3B%20every%20fifth%20file%20for%20individuals%20having%20surnames%20beginning%20with%20the%20letters%20A%2CF%20and%20R%20have%20been%20retained%20by%20the%20Archives.> .

