  rico:scopeAndContent <https://data.archives.gov.on.test.gbad.caSeries%20consists%20of%20writs%20of%20dedimus%20potestatum%20which%20were%20issued%20to%20the%20Justices%20of%20King%27s%20Bench%20prior%20to%20going%20on%20circuit.%20The%20writs%20allowed%20them%20to%20administer%20and%20take%20oaths%20of%20the%20local%20officials%2C%20and%20allowed%20them%20to%20receive%20the%20records%20of%20assize%20for%20transmission%20to%20the%20central%20court%20in%20York%20%28Toronto%29.%20These%20writs%20have%20a%20standard%20format%20signed%20by%20the%20Lieutenant-Governor%20and%20the%20Secretary%20of%20the%20Executive%20Council%20with%20the%20names%20of%20the%20Justices%20added%20to%20the%20writ.> .

