  rico:scopeAndContent <https://data.archives.gov.on.test.gbad.caSeries%20consists%20of%20case%20files%20of%20judgments%20finalizing%20civil%20actions%20brought%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20at%20Goderich%20in%20the%20County%20of%20Huron.%20Leading%20up%20to%20the%20judgment%20are%20the%20typical%20stages%20of%20an%20action%3A%20commencing%20with%20the%20writ%20of%20summons%20and%20continuing%20with%20a%20statement%20of%20claim%3B%20a%20plea%20and%20statement%20of%20defence%3B%20a%20counterclaim%20if%20applicable%3B%20various%20affidavits%20and%20supporting%20documents%3B%20the%20record%3B%20and%20any%20related%20orders.%20The%20judgment%20%28the%20decision%20or%20sentence%29%20is%20the%20culmination%20of%20the%20action.> .

