  rico:conditionsOfAccess <https://data.archives.gov.on.test.gbad.caThis%20series%20includes%20open%20and%20restricted%20records.%20Generally%2C%20the%20following%20documents%20can%20be%20made%20available%20to%20the%20public%3A%20the%20indictment%3B%20police%20information%3B%20a%20transcript%20of%20any%20public%20hearing%3B%20orders%3B%20information%20about%20the%20jury%20verdict%3B%20and%20the%20sentence.%20If%20a%20file%20is%20sealed%20by%20a%20Court%20order%2C%20it%20cannot%20be%20made%20available.%20Note%2C%20the%20following%20documents%20are%20restricted%3A%20pre-sentence%20reports%3B%20psychiatric%20information%3B%20medical%20information%3B%20exhibits%3B%20victim%20impact%20statements%3B%20and%20witness%20statements%20not%20heard%20in%20open%20court.>;
  rico:conditionsOfUse <https://data.archives.gov.on.test.gbad.caCopyright%20is%20primarily%20held%20by%20the%20Crown.%20There%20are%20no%20restrictions%20on%20reproduction.%20Permission%20of%20the%20Archives%20of%20Ontario%20is%20required%20for%20publication.>;
