  rico:scopeAndContent <https://data.archives.gov.on.test.gbad.caSeries%20consists%20of%20registers%20in%20docket%20book%20form%2C%20kept%20by%20the%20Clerk%20of%20the%20Peace%20for%20Prince%20Edward%20County%2C%20containing%20chronological%20entries%20for%20each%20minor%20criminal%20matter%20%28for%20example%2C%20breaches%20of%20liquor%20laws%2C%20traffic%20laws%2C%20malicious%20damage%20to%20property%2C%20shoplifting%20and%20keeping%20betting%20houses%2C%20amongst%20many%20other%20charges%29%20heard%20by%20the%20Magistrate%27s%20%28or%20Police%29%20Court.%20%20The%20register%20list%3A%20name%20of%20the%20prosecutor%2C%20defendant%2C%20and%20presiding%20Justice%20or%20Magistrate%3B%20charge%3B%20%20date%20and%20sentence%20of%20the%20conviction%3B%20amount%20of%20the%20fine%2C%20when%20it%20is%20to%20be%20paid%2C%20and%20to%20who%3B%20and%20the%20rationale%20for%20non-payment.%20%20The%20register%20may%20also%20contain%20accounts%2C%20consisting%20of%20financial%20records%20maintained%20by%20the%20Clerk%20of%20the%20Peace%20for%20the%20courts.> .

