  rico:isOrWasDescribedBy <https://data.archives.gov.on.test.gbad.ca/KB/ArchivalDescriptionRecord/RG%204-156>;
  rico:scopeAndContent <https://data.archives.gov.on.test.gbad.caSeries%20consists%20of%20records%20produced%20as%20part%20of%20the%20class%20action%20lawsuit%20filed%20by%20former%20residents%20of%20the%20Southwestern%20Regional%20Centre%20against%20the%20Government%20of%20Ontario%20to%20seek%20justice%20and%20compensation%20for%20abusive%20treatment%20suffered%20at%20the%20facility.%20%20The%20records%20are%20the%20documents%20produced%20and%20provided%20by%20each%20party%20to%20the%20other%20for%20the%20proceedings%20in%20accordance%20with%20civil%20procedural%20obligations%20under%20the%20Class%20Proceedings%20Act%2C%201992.%20On%20February%2024%2C%202013%2C%20the%20case%20was%20settled.%20In%20the%20settlement%20agreement%2C%20documents%20were%20ordered%20to%20be%20deposited%20at%20the%20Archives%20of%20Ontario%20for%20scholarly%20research%20purposes.%20%20The%20records%20document%20the%20operations%20of%20the%20Southwestern%20Regional%20Centre%20and%20treatment%20of%20its%20residents.%20Specific%20types%20of%20records%20include%3A%20media%20clippings%20and%20articles%2C%20government%20reports%2C%20cabinet%20documents%2C%20financial%20documents%2C%20facility%20operational%20documents%2C%20policy%20documents%2C%20correspondence%2C%20memoranda%2C%20meeting%20agendas%2C%20meeting%20minutes%2C%20briefing%20notes%2C%20directives%2C%20guidelines%2C%20agreements%2C%20notes%2C%20newsletters%2C%20log%20books%2C%20incident%20reports%2C%20guardianship%20documents%2C%20medical%20and%20behavioural%20reports%2C%20vocational%20and%20recreational%20documents%2C%20human%20resources%20records%2C%20photographs%2C%20discipline%20records%2C%20evaluations%2C%20academic%20reports%2C%20facility%20maintenance%20records%20and%20maps.> .

