  rico:scopeAndContent <https://data.archives.gov.on.test.gbad.caSeries%20consists%20of%20administrative%20records%20created%20and%2For%20maintained%20by%20the%20office%20of%20the%20Comptroller%2FGeneral%20Manager%20of%20the%20Liquor%20Control%20Board%20of%20Ontario.%20Administrative%20activities%20of%20the%20LCBO%20were%20overseen%20by%20the%20Comptroller%20from%20the%201940s%20until%201963%20when%20the%20position%20title%20was%20changed%20to%20General%20Manager.%20The%20series%20includes%20correspondence%2C%20reports%2C%20minutes%20and%20other%20administrative%20material.%20Subjects%20covered%20by%20the%20records%20include%20day-to-day%20aspects%20of%20the%20Board%27s%20operations%20such%20as%20responses%20to%20questions%20asked%20in%20the%20House%2C%20annual%20and%20financial%20reports%2C%20orders-in-council%20regarding%20employee%20appointments%2C%20price%20bulletins%2C%20and%20circulars%2C%20as%20well%20as%20correspondence%20and%20reports%20relating%20to%20liquor%20sales%2C%20warehouses%20and%20distribution.%20Documentation%20from%20various%20committees%20such%20as%20the%20Store%20Development%20Committee%20and%20Planning%20Committee%20are%20also%20included.> .

