  rico:scopeAndContent <https://data.archives.gov.on.test.gbad.caSeries%20consists%20of%20records%20created%20and%20accumulated%20by%20the%20Standing%20Committee%20on%20General%20Government.%20%20The%20types%20of%20records%20may%20include%20copies%20of%20reviews%20and%20reports%20%28final%20versions%20are%20submitted%20to%20the%20House%2C%20usually%20as%20sessional%20papers%29%20regarding%20observations%2C%20opinions%20and%20recommendations%20on%20such%20matters%20as%20legislation%3B%20budget%20estimates%3B%20all%20matters%20relating%20to%20mandate%2C%20management%2C%20organization%20or%20operations%20of%20Ministries%20and%20offices%2C%20agencies%2C%20boards%2C%20commissions%2C%20etc.%3B%20input%20from%20individuals%2C%20groups%2C%20Ministry%20officials%2C%20public%20submissions%2C%20etc.%3B%20each%20Committee%27s%20budget%20and%20expenditures%2C%20agendas%2C%20orders%20of%20reference%2C%20minutes%2C%20sub-committee%20minutes%3B%20sub-committee%20reviews%20on%20intended%20appointments%20of%20persons%20to%20agencies%2C%20boards%20and%20commissions%2C%20etc.%20%28appointee%27s%20resume%20and%20job%20descriptions%29%3B%20general%20Committee%20correspondence%2C%20House%20Leaders%27%20exhibits%2C%20background%20papers%2C%20transcripts%20and%20any%20other%20procedural%20or%20administrative%20documentation%20relating%20to%20the%20committee.> .

