  a owl:NamedIndividual .

<https://data.archives.gov.on.test.gbad.caSeries%20consists%20of%20minute%20books%20to%20serve%20as%20a%20record%20of%20cases%20heard%20by%20the%20Local%20Master%20at%20Welland.%20Entries%20typically%20record%20the%20style%20of%20cause%20in%20the%20form%20plaintiff%20versus%20defendant%2C%20the%20date%20each%20writ%20or%20other%20process%20was%20issued%2C%20the%20filing%20of%20any%20further%20proceedings%2C%20names%20of%20the%20solicitors%2C%20the%20verdict%2C%20and%20the%20costs.%20%20Cases%20include%3A%20administration%20of%20partition%20without%20action%3B%20vacating%20certificates%20of%20lis%20pendens%3B%20motions%20to%20wind%20up%20companies%3B%20motions%20for%20interpleader%3B%20payment%20into%20court%20of%20moneys%20under%20the%20Trustee%20Act%3B%20payment%20of%20money%20out%20of%20court%3B%20hearing%20motions%20for%20judgment%20on%20specially%20endorsed%20writs%20and%20actions%20for%20account%3B%20certain%20motions%20relating%20to%20estates.>
  a owl:NamedIndividual .

<https://data.archives.gov.on.test.gbad.caSeries%20consists%20of%20municipal%20procurement%20bylaws%20and%20policies%20for%20the%20following%20regions%3A%20Atikokan%2C%20Dryden%2C%20Halton%2C%20Kenora%2C%20London%2C%20Mississauga%2C%20Orillia%2C%20Oshawa%2C%20Ottawa%2C%20Owen%20Sound%2C%20Peel%20Region%2C%20Quinte%20West%2C%20St.%20Catharines%2C%20Simcoe%20County%2C%20Thunder%20Bay%2C%20Toronto%2C%20Waterloo.%20%20%20Series%20also%20includes%20iner-provincial%20trade%20agreements%20and%20procurement%20guides.>
