  a owl:NamedIndividual .

<https://data.archives.gov.on.test.gbad.caSeries%20consists%20of%20property%20management%20and%20lease%20and%20license%20files%20pertaining%20to%20Ontario%20Heritage%20Foundation%20%28OHF%29%20properties.%20The%20records%20are%20created%2C%20received%2C%20and%20used%20by%20the%20Heritage%20Programs%20Branch%20to%20ensure%20that%20OHF%20properties%20are%20maintained%20to%20standard.%20%20Records%20include%20leases%2C%20licenses%2C%20past%20and%20current%20agreements%2C%20correspondence%2C%20board%20minutes%2C%20background%20information%2C%20insurance%20documents%2C%20work%20orders%2C%20tax%20documents%2C%20feasibility%20studies%2C%20and%20future%20use%20studies.%20%20Correspondents%20include%20legal%20counsel%2C%20the%20tenant%2C%20and%20contractors%20for%20repairs.%20%20The%20files%20are%20arranged%20alphabetically%20by%20property.>
