<https://data.archives.gov.on.test.gbad.caSeries%20consists%20of%20published%20material%20that%20Goldschmidt%20collected%20for%20personal%20interest%20and%20research.%20Subject%20matter%20includes%20possible%20festivals%2C%20the%20need%20for%20a%20National%20Centre%20of%20the%20Performing%20Arts%2C%20the%20Canadian%20Conference%20for%20the%20Arts%20seminar%20in%201965%2C%20and%20the%20Centennial%20Commission.%20There%20are%20also%20a%20few%20information%20releases%20about%20the%20death%20of%20Sir%20Winston%20Churchill.%20Also%20included%20is%20the%20musical%20score%2C%20commissioned%20by%20Goldschmidt%2C%20to%20the%20play%20Jezebel%20by%20Robertson%20Davies.%20Dr.%20Goldschmidt%20has%20made%20notes%20in%20some%20of%20the%20material.>
