<https://data.archives.gov.on.test.gbad.caSeries%20consists%20of%20records%20maintained%20by%20the%20Policy%20and%20Planning%20Coordination%20Office%20pertaining%20to%20meetings%20and%20activities%20of%20the%20Council%20of%20Ministers%20of%20Education.%20Records%20include%20minutes%20of%20Council%20and%20the%20Council%27s%20Advisory%20Committee%20of%20Deputy%20Ministers%27%20meetings%20as%20well%20as%20other%20related%20files.>
  a owl:NamedIndividual .

<https://data.archives.gov.on.test.gbad.caSeries%20consists%20of%20records%20of%20the%20Records%20of%20the%20Commission%20of%20Inquiry%20Into%20Matters%20Relating%20to%20the%20Sale%20and%20Distribution%20of%20Fruits%20and%20Vegetables%2C%20which%20examined%20allegations%20of%20irregular%20brockerage%20payments%20by%20suppliers%20and%20purchasers%20of%20fruits%20and%20vegetables.%20%20The%20series%20contains%20the%20final%20report%2C%20transcripts%2C%20correspondence%2C%20investigation%20notes%2C%20newspaper%20clippings%2C%20some%20exhibits%20and%20briefs%20and%20related%20miscellaneous%20documents.%20%20The%20transcripts%20are%20chronologically%20arranged%20while%20the%20exhibits%20and%20correspondence%20are%20arranged%20alphabetically%20by%20the%20name%20of%20the%20respondent.>
