<https://data.archives.gov.on.test.gbad.caSub-series%20consists%20of%20a%20single%20volume%20entitled%20%20%22Warrants%20for%20lands%20without%20purchase%2C%20Regulations%2021%20November%201825%22.%20%20In%20point%20of%20fact%2C%20this%20one%20volume%20contains%20two%20separate%20registers.%20%20The%20first%20part%20of%20the%20volume%20consists%20of%20a%20register%20of%20fiats%20for%20leases%2C%20covering%20the%20period%201830%20%28lease%20%23%20926%29%20to%20April%201860%20%28lease%20%23%201688%29.%20%20Entries%20record%3A%20%20the%20Surveyor%20General%27s%20fiat%20number%3B%20the%20Executive%20Council%20Office%27s%20number%3B%20the%20Attorney%20General%27s%20number%3B%20the%20name%2C%20occupation%20and%20place%20of%20residence%20of%20the%20leasee%3B%20location%20of%20the%20land%20being%20leased%20%28township%2C%20concession%20and%20lot%29%3B%20the%20type%20of%20reserve%20being%20leased%20%28e.g.%2C%20water%20lot%2C%20clergy%20reserve%29%3B%20the%20date%20of%20the%20order-in-%20council%20authorising%20the%20lease%3B%20the%20date%20rent%20payments%20are%20to%20commence%3B%20the%20date%20of%20the%20Attorney%20General%27s%20fiat%3B%20a%20description%20number%20%28these%20description%20numbers%20have%20the%20letter%20%22L%22%20as%20a%20suffix%29%3B%20and%20remarks.%20%20An%20alphabetical%20index%20to%20leasees%20is%20located%20at%20the%20back%20of%20this%20volume.%20%20The%20second%20part%20of%20the%20volume%20is%20entitled%3A%20%20%22Warrants%20for%20lands%20without%20purchase%20under%20regulations%20of%2021%20November%201825%2C%20commencing%201%20January%201826%22.%20%20Entries%20in%20the%20volume%20record%3A%20%20the%20warrant%20number%3B%20the%20name%2C%20place%20of%20residence%2C%20place%20of%20birth%2C%20and%20occupation%20of%20the%20grantee%3B%20the%20date%20of%20the%20order-in-council%20authorising%20the%20grant%3B%20the%20acreage%20granted%20and%20the%20district%20in%20which%20it%20was%20to%20be%20located%3B%20the%20location%20of%20the%20grant%20%28lot%2C%20concession%20and%20township%29%3B%20the%20date%20the%20ticket%20of%20location%20was%20issued%2C%20and%20to%20whom%3B%20the%20Attorney%20General%27s%20fiat%20number%20and%20date%3B%20and%20a%20description%20number.%20Entries%20cover%20warrant%20%23%201%20%281826%29%20to%20%23%20182%20%281828%29.%20%20Some%20entries%20contain%20later%20annotations%20relating%20to%20the%20grants%2C%20to%201832.>
  a owl:NamedIndividual .

