<https://data.archives.gov.on.test.gbad.caThe%20donor%20has%20transferred%20copyright%20to%20the%20Archives%20of%20Ontario%2C%20insofar%20as%20he%20owns%20it.%20Series%20may%20also%20contain%20material%20owned%20by%20various%20other%20copyright%20owners.%20To%20find%20out%20more%20about%20the%20copyright%20status%20of%20the%20material%20you%20wish%20to%20use%2C%20consult%20a%20Reference%20Archivist%20through%20the%20Reference%20Desk.%20There%20are%20no%20restrictions%20on%20reproduction%20for%20research%20and%20private%20study.%20%20If%20you%20wish%20to%20use%20the%20material%20for%20purposes%20other%20than%20research%20and%20private%20study%2C%20please%20submit%20a%20Request%20for%20Permission%20to%20Publish%2C%20Exhibit%2C%20or%20Broadcast%20Form.>
  a owl:NamedIndividual .

