<https://data.archives.gov.on.test.gbad.caThis%20series%20consists%20of%20two%20sets%20of%20plans%2C%20elevations%2C%20sections%20and%20three%20detail%20sheets%20for%20Knox%20Presbyterian%20Church%2C%20located%20on%20City%20Hall%20Square%20in%20Ottawa%2C%20Ontario%2C%20at%20the%20site%20of%20the%20present%20National%20Arts%20Centre.%20The%20design%20was%20realised%20in%201874%20and%20demolished%20May%2025%2C%201938.>
